{"tid":420510,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍緊拖同無拍拖既你 入一入黎傾2句","createTime":"2017-10-01T12:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T20:32:54.000Z","uid":129349,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f473087c825338a0e2a794e62bb6ee6a0f9460b","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"你地覺得一開始拍拖個時講唔講得上好愛對方？定只係單純咁好中意？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開始就已經係愛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要相處下發展下先會到愛，然後想過人世<br />\n<br />\n負評個d可唔可以講下通常要拍幾耐先會知自己唔止係中意而係愛？"},{"pid":"b3d8f68e6efbe834d3bb4d07a64ca9d72c15fbfc","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1362be541df5febb30b8e27f2d3fd6ad72a8f6c2","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"同個ex岩岩分手無耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話佢好中意我但係佢覺得我唔係可以同佢一世既人<br />\n因為一齊左6個月佢都無好強烈愛既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我覺得6個月其實好短，同埋點解而家大家都仲中意但就要分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話相處愈來只會更加唔捨得分手<br />\n<br />\n巴打們，係咪所有男人都會以諗將來為先，覺得無以後，就算而家幾中意都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4cef466981a0123619657f1c069ea2d7f5c107","tid":420510,"uid":8727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"可能越拍越發現對方缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876fe377cde307ce2effb9970cbd24ed8e5dfaf4","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能越拍越發現對方缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都有講過一開始覺得我好完美，<br />\n但係慢慢發現我都有d好無理頭既脾氣<br />\n但男人係咪唔明<br />\n女人愈在乎愈中意<br />\n就會愈小氣，<br />\n但其實一句 唔好咁啦錫哂你啦<br />\n就好快無事<br />\n但佢偏偏唔係，會中意同我嗌到底<br />\n雖然之後佢都會同我講翻對唔住，係自己唔夠細心"},{"pid":"e26172cea4a15b44a0bd8a95bb0ead9c48b0611e","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:03:50.000Z","msg":"入黎傾下計好無，好頹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b78dabb6c960ccae478df23c446fbd18b38e85","tid":420510,"uid":83956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"我依家預到嘅情況就係咁<br />\n前2個ex都係一開始就好愛 有心跳加速個種感覺 算係love at first sight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前2日被表白 我清楚係對佢有好感同鐘意嘅<br />\n但係真係無個種好愛嘅感覺 亦到唔知去唔去到/幾時先去到個個位<br />\n好怕一齊會辜負咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411b20780bc8e083362fb0d74c35a1116ffa0a5d","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我依家預到嘅情況就係咁<br />\n前2個ex都係一開始就好愛 有心跳加速個種感覺 算係love at first sight <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前2日被表白 我清楚係對佢有好感同鐘意嘅<br />\n但係真係無個種好愛嘅感覺 亦到唔知去唔去到/幾時先去到個個位<br />\n好怕一齊會辜負咗佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得要enjoy大家都中意對方既moment<br />\n人海茫茫，遇到有feel既人已經好難<br />\n對方都對你有相同既感覺係幾咁難得<br />\n咪試左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbc7534d40f25ddf41fd7fa07fb0e08e28fd5a6","tid":420510,"uid":129349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"負皮個d可唔可以講下，你講得幾耐先會去到愛個個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbaa69538dca95eec6d8707d35c081098a0b51d","tid":420510,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"一開始本身諗住玩下試下先<br />\n到分手嗰一下就知原來自己比對方